setMarsFileIsClosed

public boolean setMarsFileIsClosed()
Closes the file for the calling thread. If the calling thread is not the last reader/writer that has the file's "handle", the file is not really closed, but calling thread is removed from the readingthread list.

Returns:
true if the file has been closed, false elsewhere
